<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Portal Enfermagem</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --primary: #a51b0b;
      --primary-2: #000000;
      --text: #000000;
      --muted: #222222;
      --line: #000000;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .topbar {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a51b0b 0%, #6f1208 45%, #160504 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }
    .topbar-inner {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .brand {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .auth a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .auth a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .topbar-controls {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .topbar-btn {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .topbar-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.22); }
    .nav {
      background: var(--primary-2);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 10px 18px;
    }
    .nav a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .container {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 22px auto;
      padding: 0 18px;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #a51b0b, #000000);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }
    .hero h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 30px; }
    .hero p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }
    .card .value {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .section {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 18px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .section h3 { margin-top: 0; }
    .links {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .links a {
      display: block;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #000000;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px;
      color: #000000;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .links a:hover { background: #f5f5f5; }
    .muted { color: var(--muted); }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 24px 0 30px;
    }
    .guest-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #a51b0b, #000000);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }
    .guest-hero p { margin: 0 0 12px; }
    .guest-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #7a1408;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .guest-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .guest-card {
      border: 1px solid #000000;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .guest-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      height: 140px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .guest-card p {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <% const usuarioLocal = (typeof usuario !== 'undefined' && usuario) ? usuario : null; %>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-inner">
      <h1 class="brand">Portal Enfermagem</h1>
      <nav class="auth">
        <% if (usuarioLocal) { %>
          <a href="/usuario">Minha Conta</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/login">Entrar</a>
          <a href="/cadastro">Cadastre-se</a>
        <% } %>
      </nav>
      <div class="topbar-controls">
        <button type="button" class="topbar-btn" onclick="history.back()">Voltar</button>
        <% if (usuarioLocal) { %>
          <a class="topbar-btn" href="/sair">Sair</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a class="topbar-btn" href="/login">Entrar</a>
        <% } %>

      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  
  <main class="container">
    <% if (!usuarioLocal) { %>
      <section class="guest-hero">
        <h2>Seu apoio rápido na prática de enfermagem</h2>
        <p>Veja conteúdos introdutórios e exemplos visuais. Para acessar todos os módulos, faça login.</p>
        <a class="guest-cta" href="/login">Entrar e acessar tudo</a>
      </section>

      <section class="guest-grid" aria-label="Prévia de conteúdos">
        <div class="guest-card">
          <img src="/site/img/product01.png" alt="Prévia de procedimentos">
          <p>Protocolos essenciais em poucos cliques</p>
        </div>
        <div class="guest-card">
          <img src="/site/img/product02.png" alt="Prévia de medicamentos">
          <p>Medicamentos organizados por classe</p>
        </div>
        <div class="guest-card">
          <img src="/site/img/product03.png" alt="Prévia de terminologias">
          <p>Termos e definições para revisão rápida</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    <% } else { %>
      <section class="hero">
        <h2>Seu apoio rápido na prática de enfermagem</h2>
        <p>Consulte conteúdos essenciais, revise protocolos, teste conhecimentos e organize sua rotina em um só lugar.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="grid" aria-label="Resumo">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Procedimentos</h3>
          <div class="value"><%= procedimentoCount %></div>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Medicamentos</h3>
          <div class="value"><%= medicamentoCount %></div>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Terminologias</h3>
          <div class="value"><%= termoCount %></div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h3>Acessos rápidos</h3>
        <p class="muted">Abra direto o recurso que você precisa no momento.</p>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="/procedimentos">Consultar procedimentos</a>
          <a href="/medicamentos">Consultar medicamentos</a>
          <a href="/terminologias">Ver terminologias</a>
          <a href="/quiz">Responder quiz</a>
          <a href="/lembretes">Gerenciar lembretes</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    <% } %>

    <div class="footer">Portal Enfermagem</div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
